  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It carried the bundles and the luggage, whatever we brought along, from the trains and-- pulled by two horses, this wagon had rubber tires.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as it began to pass us, we noticed that [NON-ENGLISH] was sitting in the back of it, looking for us in the rows as it pass, was passing us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she was sitting in the back with her feet dangling down as she did this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she, when she saw us, she just hopped off and joined us in the row, and she continued to walk with us in the direction that the wagon was going.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Nobody noticed her in the hoopla, in the big commotion, and-- but Mother was concerned and-- because she was afraid that [NON-ENGLISH] will not be able to keep up with us while we would have to work very hard.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But of course, we were also happy to have the family together, at least the three of us, so we continued to walk and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were taken to a place where they, where they shaved our heads completely with a hand-operated hair-cutting machine, whatever they are called.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in a minute, my hair was gone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "First, first, they actually snipped off my braids, and they just dumped it on that pile.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then they took this, these-- I wish I knew the word for it-- hair-cutting device, and they just went through my head.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I couldn't believe that my, my hair was completely gone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And as I touched it, I noticed a little blood on my hand because they did it so fast they cut into the scalp a little bit, which, nothing to complain about, but I thought I'd mention it because it, it was very crudely done.",
      "word_count": 45
    }
  ],
